headline: Deutsche Bank sees ‘risk-on’ setup for retail in 2026, favors AS and ROST
summary: Investing.com -- Deutsche Bank resumed coverage of retail stocks with a broadly constructive outlook for 2026, citing solid top-line momentum, improved consumer conditions and easing policy headwinds.

headline: The Zacks Analyst Blog Highlights Five Below, American Eagle Outfitters, The Gap and Ulta Beauty
summary: Five Below, American Eagle, Gap and Ulta Beauty stand out as retail winners for 2026 as easing inflation and omnichannel strength support growth.

headline: How PayPal’s New Transaction Graph Analytics Program Will Impact PayPal Holdings (PYPL) Investors
summary: In early January 2026, PayPal launched its Transaction Graph Insights & Measurement program, giving merchants and advertisers a cross-merchant view of real shopper behavior, campaign performance, and data-driven recommendations using transaction data from more than 430 million consumer accounts and tens of millions of merchants.
